flowchart TB
  A[Patch Preview<br/>CSV + MD + diff] --> B{{Human Diff Review}}
  B -->|approved| C[Backup Chapters]
  B -.rejected / revise.-> A
  C --> D[Apply<br/>SHA-checked, LF write]
  D --> E[guard-no-auto-verified<br/>+ smoke-test]
  E -->|pass| F[(Apply Report)]
  E -.fail.-> G[Rollback from Backup]
  G -.-> A
